article_title: Photos: Members of two Milwaukee-area churches make a trip to Assisi in Rome
article_text: Area teens from Christ Church Episcopal in Whitefish Bay and All Peoples Lutheran Church in Milwaukee will make a joint pilgrimage to Assisi over the next week. The two groups have invested a lot of effort building a relationship between the very disparate communities.
